::Stasis pod:: 

::It was slicing through the atmosphere like a knife through butter.  The 
heat from the force of the stasis pod ripping through the atmosphere was 
intense, but the pod remained intact.  It finally went straight through the 
atmosphere, and onto god's green earth.  It landed in Spain, right next to 
the Iron fist.::
